history.content:
Hi everyone!

We’re looking for qualified students to join Data 100 course staff next semester. We’re hiring for both readers and TAs.

To apply, make sure you’ve filled out the official department application (https://deptapps.coe.berkeley.edu/ase/eecs/apply). In addition, you need to fill out our supplemental application (http://tinyurl.com/data100app). The deadline to fill out the supplemental form in order to be considered for an interview is this Tuesday at 11:59pm. We will try to hold interviews later this week.

Feel free to reach out at data100.instructors@berkeley.edu with any questions!
